Author: gabbyph1201
Text: My heart aches for you. I’m in the exact same boat right now.. 100% same situation I’m so sorry. I wish I could offer u help but I’m afraid I’m in the exact same place. I’m so sorry I wouldn’t wish this upon anyone I feel for u
